<%
  const breadcrumbs = [
    { name: "Home", href: "/" },
    { name: "ERF EC12 Lorry Hearse", href: "/erf-ec12-hearse" }
  ];
%>

<%- include('partials/head', {
  title,
  metaTitle: 'ERF EC12 Lorry Hearse Hire UK | PNW Carriage Masters',
  metaDescription: 'Explore our ERF EC12 lorry hearse for funerals across the UK. A distinctive British classic truck hearse for a fitting final journey.',
  canonicalPath,
  breadcrumbs
}) %>

<%- include('partials/header') %>

<%
  const s = settings || {};
  const phoneRaw = String(s.phone || "").trim();
  const phoneTel = phoneRaw.replace(/\s+/g, "");
  const erfFile = String(s.erf_ec12_img || "").trim();
  const erfVer  = String(s.erf_ec12_ver || "").trim();
%>

<div class="wrap">
<%- include('partials/breadcrumbs', { breadcrumbs }) %>
  <div class="card">
    <h1 style="color: var(--accent);">ERF EC12 Lorry Hearse</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Our ERF EC12 lorry hearse is a distinctive specialist funeral vehicle, designed for funerals where families want a final journey with individuality, character and real presence.
    </p>

    <div class="cta" style="margin:18px 0 8px;">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Enquire about this hearse</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/gallery">View gallery</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/case-studies">Case studies</a>
      <% if (phoneTel) { %>
        <a class="btn" href="tel:<%= phoneTel %>">Call <%= phoneRaw %></a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <% if (erfFile) { %>
    <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
      <img
        src="/uploads/<%= erfFile %>?v=<%= erfVer %>"
        alt="ERF EC12 lorry hearse for funeral hire across the UK"
        style="display:block; width:100%; max-width:560px; margin:0 auto; border-radius:16px;"
      >
    </div>
  <% } %>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Technical specifications</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Model:</strong> Classic ERF EC Olympic</p>
      <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Year of manufacture:</strong> 1999</p>
      <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Edition:</strong> Olympic Gold, top of the range in its day</p>
      <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Built in:</strong> Sandbach, Cheshire</p>
      <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Colour:</strong> Factory Black</p>
      <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Engine:</strong> Caterpillar C12</p>
      <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Transmission:</strong> 8 speed</p>
      <p><strong style="color: var(--accent);">Hearse conversion:</strong> 2018</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0;">
        <strong style="color: var(--accent);">Additional extras:</strong>
        Super singles fitted to front, Air horns, External music system, Bespoke aluminium body, Factory side skirts.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">A distinctive ERF EC12 lorry hearse</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        The ERF EC12 offers a striking and respectful alternative to a traditional hearse. It is especially suited to funerals where families want the final journey to reflect a loved one’s connection to trucks, transport, engineering, heavy vehicles or life on the road.
      </p>
      <p>
        As part of our specialist fleet, the ERF EC12 helps create a memorable and personal tribute without losing the dignity and professionalism that matter on the day of the funeral.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Who this hearse often suits</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        The ERF EC12 can be especially fitting for someone with a strong link to British trucking, haulage, logistics, plant, engineering, recovery or road transport. It is often chosen when a family wants the vehicle itself to feel like a meaningful part of the tribute.
      </p>
      <p>
        For many people, the ERF name carries its own identity and heritage, which makes this hearse particularly personal for families wanting a final journey connected to a true British classic truck.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Why families choose the ERF EC12</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        A specialist hearse like the ERF EC12 is often chosen because it feels more personal than a conventional funeral vehicle. For someone whose life or interests were closely connected to haulage or heavy vehicles, it can be a fitting and meaningful choice.
      </p>
      <p>
        The vehicle becomes part of the tribute, helping the funeral feel individual, memorable and true to the person being remembered.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">What to expect on the day</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        Our ERF EC12 lorry hearse is supplied to work alongside the funeral director and the wider funeral arrangements already in place. The aim is always to provide a specialist vehicle that complements the day professionally, respectfully and with the right presence.
      </p>
      <p>
        Timing, route, venue access and the overall tone of the service all matter. The ERF EC12 is provided as part of a dignified final journey, not simply as a display vehicle.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Working with funeral directors</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        Our specialist hearses are supplied exclusively for the funeral profession. We work with funeral directors to confirm availability, discuss location and service details, and help ensure the chosen vehicle is suitable for the funeral plans.
      </p>
      <p>
        This helps give funeral directors and families confidence that the ERF EC12 will be a fitting and dependable part of the day’s arrangements.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Funeral hire across the UK</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        Our ERF EC12 lorry hearse is available for funeral hire across the UK mainland. We are based near Chester, close to North Wales and North West England, but can provide specialist hearse hire much further afield depending on the date, the location and the vehicle required.
      </p>
      <p>
        For pricing, availability and guidance on whether the ERF EC12 is the right fit for a funeral, please contact us directly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Related gallery and case studies</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        You can explore more ERF EC12 images on our <a href="/gallery">gallery page</a> and view recent field updates on our <a href="/case-studies">case studies page</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        These pages help show how our specialist hearses are used in real funeral settings and how a lorry hearse can become a meaningful part of a personal final journey.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Frequently asked questions about this hearse</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p><strong>Is the ERF EC12 available across the UK?</strong><br>
        Yes. Availability depends on the date, the location and the overall funeral arrangements, so early enquiry is always helpful.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Who usually books this hearse?</strong><br>
        The vehicle is supplied for the funeral profession and is typically arranged as part of the funeral director’s plans for the service.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Why is this hearse especially popular?</strong><br>
        It is often chosen because of its strong British trucking identity and its suitability for funerals where the final journey should reflect a life connected to haulage, engineering or the road.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0;"><strong>Where can I find out more?</strong><br>
        You can also visit our <a href="/faq">FAQ page</a> or contact us directly to discuss availability and suitability.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title">Related pages</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p><a href="/renault-magnum-hearse">Renault Magnum hearse</a></p>
      <p><a href="/lorry-hearse-hire-uk">Lorry hearse hire across the UK</a></p>
      <p><a href="/truck-hearse-vs-traditional-hearse">Truck hearse vs traditional hearse</a></p>
      <p><a href="/case-studies">Truck hearse case studies</a></p>
      <p><a href="/gallery">Gallery</a></p>
      <p><a href="/faq">FAQ</a></p>
      <p><a href="/contact">Contact</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--accent);">Enquire about the ERF EC12 lorry hearse</h2>
    <div class="rich">
      <p>
        If you would like to discuss availability, location or whether the ERF EC12 is the right fit for an upcoming funeral, please contact us directly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cta" style="margin:18px 0 0;">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Contact us</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/gallery">View gallery</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/case-studies">View case studies</a>
      <% if (phoneTel) { %>
        <a class="btn" href="tel:<%= phoneTel %>">Call <%= phoneRaw %></a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
